    <description>A unique silenced rifle, designed for stealthier operations while in confined areas. A maxim silencer was put on this rifle to reduce the noise that this weapon makes.\n\nA rather generic rifle, moreso meant for hunting animals. It'll still get the job done on whatever you throw at it.\n\nHis voice grew louder in my ear."Steady your breathing, you won't catch your prey if you keep misaligning your shots." He held the long end of my barrel up for me, guiding it to a target.\n\n"There are dozens of them. Take your shot at the least dangerous one." He gestured toward the nearest target.\n\nI fired, my finger pressing down on the trigger. The man dropped dead, a clean headshot leaving his brain matter against the wall. Nobody was around to hear the body.\n\nHis voice grew noticably quieter. "Good. Now get rid of the rest before they find their buddy."\n\nWhen I had finally killed the last bug in the outpost, nobody was left standing next to me. The whispers in my ear had disappeared, leaving nothing but the cold wind and ambience of the cave to fill my ears.</description>
